  <brief_title>Closure of Anastomotic Leaks in the Stomach and Esophagus by Endoscopic Suturing</brief_title>
  <acronym>GASTROSUTURE</acronym>
  <official_title>Safety and Efficacy of Closure of Postoperative Anastomotic Leaks in the Stomach and Esophagus by Endoscopic Suturing: A Prospective Pilot Study</official_title>
